Class ManifestApplicationInformationProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.communote.server.core.application.ManifestApplicationInformationProvider
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ApplicationInformation, ApplicationInformationProvider

    public class ManifestApplicationInformationProvider
extends Object
implements ApplicationInformationProvider, ApplicationInformation
    Retrieves the information from the Manifest file of the application. The Manifest is loaded from the directory where the application got extracted to.
    Author:
    Communote GmbH - http://www.communote.com/
